<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Lab Experiment Failure Mystery</title>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <header>
      <h1>Lab Experiment Failure Mystery</h1>
      <p>
        You are investigating a failed experiment at NovaChem Research Lab.
        Something went wrong during a late-night reactor test, and the records do not match.
        Search for clues, question the suspects, and solve the case.
      </p>
      <p id="progressText">Clues found: 0 / 5</p>
    </header>

    <main>
      <section id="search-lab">
        <h2>1. Search the Lab</h2>
        <p>Click each area to uncover clues.</p>

        <div class="lab-grid">
          <button class="clue-btn" data-clue="computer">💻 Computer Terminal</button>
          <button class="clue-btn" data-clue="locker">🔐 Storage Locker</button>
          <button class="clue-btn" data-clue="camera">📹 Security Camera</button>
          <button class="clue-btn" data-clue="sample">🧪 Chemical Sample</button>
          <button class="clue-btn" data-clue="logbook">📓 Lab Logbook</button>
        </div>

        <div id="clueDisplay">
          <h3>Clue Details</h3>
          <p>Select a lab area to reveal a clue.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="interview-suspects">
        <h2>2. Interview Suspects</h2>
        <p>Select a suspect to read their statement.</p>

        <div class="suspect-grid">
          <button class="suspect-btn" data-suspect="drlee">
            Dr. Lee<br />
            <small>Lead Scientist</small>
          </button>

          <button class="suspect-btn" data-suspect="maya">
            Maya<br />
            <small>Lab Assistant</small>
          </button>

          <button class="suspect-btn" data-suspect="owen">
            Owen<br />
            <small>Safety Officer</small>
          </button>
        </div>

        <div id="suspectDisplay">
          <h3>Suspect Statement</h3>
          <p>Select a suspect to view their statement.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="solve-case">
        <h2>3. Solve the Mystery</h2>
        <p>Answer the questions once you have reviewed the clues.</p>

        <div class="question-group">
          <h3>Question 1: What caused the failure?</h3>
          <button class="answer-btn" data-question="q1" data-value="a">
            A cooling system glitch caused random overheating.
          </button>
          <button class="answer-btn" data-question="q1" data-value="b">
            The wrong chemical was deliberately used to hide a mistake.
          </button>
          <button class="answer-btn" data-question="q1" data-value="c">
            A power outage corrupted the experiment settings.
          </button>
        </div>

        <div class="question-group">
          <h3>Question 2: Who was most responsible?</h3>
          <button class="answer-btn" data-question="q2" data-value="a">Dr. Lee</button>
          <button class="answer-btn" data-question="q2" data-value="b">Maya</button>
          <button class="answer-btn" data-question="q2" data-value="c">Owen</button>
        </div>

        <div class="question-group">
          <h3>Question 3: Why did they do it?</h3>
          <button class="answer-btn" data-question="q3" data-value="a">
            To sabotage the company for a competitor.
          </button>
          <button class="answer-btn" data-question="q3" data-value="b">
            To cover up that the experiment protocol was skipped.
          </button>
          <button class="answer-btn" data-question="q3" data-value="c">
            To steal research data during the chaos.
          </button>
        </div>

        <button id="submitBtn">Submit Case Report</button>
      </section>

      <section id="resultBox">
        <h2>Case Result</h2>
        <p>Your investigation result will appear here.</p>
      </section>
    </main>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
